  "body": "When adding validators, the duties for those validators could be re-calculated to reduce the time taken for the new validator to start attesting.\n\nWhen removing validators, the duties for the removed validators could be removed from the pending duties list, as we know that they don't need to be performed as soon as the deletion is successful.\n",
